OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784432922
OL,3,CBurnham to scrap digital ID to focus
OL,4,Con cost of living in 'reset of
OL,5,Cpriorities'
OL,7,FAndy Burnham will scrap Sir Keir
OL,8,FStarmer's flagship digital ID
OL,9,Fprogramme for all adults when he
OL,10,Fbecomes prime minister on Monday.
OL,12,FBurnham's office described the move as
OL,13,Fa "reset", with money earmarked
OL,14,Fshifted to focus on "the daily
OL,15,Fpriorities facing people across the
OL,16,Fcountry".
OL,18,FA spokesman for the incoming PM said
OL,19,Fhis government would spend time and
OL,20,Fresources where it's most needed, such
OL,21,Fas helping with the cost of living.
OL,26,@uD@COUuD@IO]vD@UOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784432922
OL,3,CBurnham to scrap digital ID to focus
OL,4,Con cost of living in 'reset of
OL,5,Cpriorities'
OL,7,FThe Office for Budget Responsibility
OL,8,Festimated last November that the
OL,9,Fprogramme would cost #1.8 billion over
OL,10,Fthree years.
OL,12,FDowning Street rejected this figure
OL,13,Fbut did not provide an estimate of its
OL,14,Fown, which a parliamentary committee
OL,15,Fnoted earlier this year left open the
OL,16,Fpossibility it could be more.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784432922
OL,3,CBurnham to scrap digital ID to focus
OL,4,Con cost of living in 'reset of
OL,5,Cpriorities'
OL,7,FSir Keir announced digital ID plans
OL,8,Fahead of last year's Labour
OL,9,Fconference, saying it would be
OL,10,Fmandatory for right-to-work checks as
OL,11,Fpart of a crackdown on illegal
OL,12,Fimmigration.
OL,14,FMinisters expected the programme to go
OL,15,Ffurther, becoming the "bedrock of the
OL,16,Fmodern state" in a system of
OL,17,F"government by app".
OL,26,@wD@WOUxD@MO]yD@AOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784432922
OL,3,CBurnham to scrap digital ID to focus
OL,4,Con cost of living in 'reset of
OL,5,Cpriorities'
OL,7,FBut support for digital IDs collapsed
OL,8,Fafter Sir Keir announced the plans,
OL,9,Fand ministers later said it would be
OL,10,Fvoluntary for right-to-work checks.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FShadow technology secretary Julia
OL,18,FLopez said: "Labour have wasted
OL,19,Fmillions of pounds on this project and
OL,20,Fnow Andy Burnham is trying to pretend
OL,21,Fhe's riding to the rescue.
OL,26,@zD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784432922
OL,3,CBurnham to scrap digital ID to focus
OL,4,Con cost of living in 'reset of
OL,5,Cpriorities'
OL,7,F"After pressure from the
OL,8,FConservatives, mandatory ID was
OL,9,Falready apparently off the table. Andy
OL,10,FBurnham now needs to explain whether
OL,11,Fthat was untrue, or whether he is
OL,12,Fsimply claiming credit for a decision
OL,13,Fthat had already been taken.
OL,15,F"Andy Burnham should stop the
OL,16,Fpolitical theatre and be clear about
OL,17,Fwhat exactly he is scrapping. Only the
OL,18,FConservatives have the team and the
OL,19,Fplan to restore common sense to public
OL,20,Fpolicy."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784432922
OL,3,CBurnham to scrap digital ID to focus
OL,4,Con cost of living in 'reset of
OL,5,Cpriorities'
OL,7,FLib Dem Cabinet Office spokeswoman
OL,8,FLisa Smart described it as "a huge win
OL,9,Ffor all those who have fought tooth
OL,10,Fand nail to stop the Government from
OL,11,Fpushing through its doomed mandatory
OL,12,Fdigital ID scheme".
OL,14,FJack Coulson, head of advocacy at Big
OL,15,FBrother Watch, welcomed the decision
OL,16,Fwhich marks the first major break from
OL,17,FSir Keir's policies that Burnham has
OL,18,Fconfirmed before taking office.
OL,26,@pD@\OUtD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
