OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784432922
OL,3,CBurnham to scrap digital ID to focus
OL,4,Con cost of living in 'reset of
OL,5,Cpriorities'
OL,7,FHe is expected to provide further
OL,8,Fdetail of his plans on Monday after
OL,9,Fvisiting Buckingham Palace to "kiss
OL,10,Fhands" with King Charles and then
OL,11,Fformally invited to enter No 10.
OL,13,FAllies have said he intends to make a
OL,14,F"dynamic start" to his premiership and
OL,15,Fhe is expected to use a speech to set
OL,16,Fout plans on the cost of living and
OL,17,Fhighlight his core theme of devolving
OL,18,Fpower from Whitehall to regions across
OL,19,Fthe UK.
OL,26,@qD@_OUrD@FO]vD@AOUvD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
