PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784432922
OL,3,CBurnham to scrap digital ID to focus
OL,4,Con cost of living in 'reset of
OL,5,Cpriorities'
OL,7,FReports have suggested he could be
OL,8,Fpreparing to break with another of Sir
OL,9,FKeir's policies and approve further
OL,10,Foil and gas drilling in the North Sea.
OL,12,FBurnham has pledged to reach out to
OL,13,Fother parties and end a culture of
OL,14,Fpolitical "point scoring" at
OL,15,FWestminster.
OL,17,FBut Badenoch said she would "score as
OL,18,Fmany points as possible if it means
OL,19,Fthe right thing for the country".
OL,26,@vD@KOUvD@YO]yD@]OU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
